{
  "archetypeKey": "echo_fox",
  "displayName": "墨影狐",
  "slots": {
    "kaomoji": [
      "(瞥你一眼)",
      "(尾尖一闪)",
      "(别开脸)",
      "(尾尖冷光明灭)",
      "(挑了挑眉)",
      "(尾巴轻轻扫过你手背)",
      "(冷光暗了一下)",
      "(假装没看见你)"
    ],
    "food": [
      "腌渍小鱼",
      "一小碟野莓",
      "薄切的鹿脯",
      "夜里抓的萤虫",
      "精致的山栗",
      "半块烟熏小肉",
      "一撮野蜂蜜"
    ],
    "treat": [
      "琥珀色的小硬糖",
      "三粒坚果仁",
      "腌过的酸果干",
      "一小片冰镇梨",
      "讲究的桂花糕"
    ],
    "activity": [
      "解谜",
      "夜巡",
      "藏东西",
      "数尾尖的冷光",
      "在暗处布一道机关",
      "把谜珠转着玩",
      "盯着影子发呆"
    ],
    "endearment": [
      "你",
      "凡人",
      "笨手笨脚的家伙",
      "好奇的人类",
      "慢半拍的家伙",
      "你这种人"
    ],
    "mutter": [
      "……无趣。",
      "这点小事也值得高兴。",
      "哼，被我看穿了。",
      "差一步,就差一步。",
      "夜还长着呢。",
      "谜底我早就知道了。",
      "你们人类总是这么吵。",
      "……懒得理。"
    ]
  },
  "lines": [
    {
      "id": "echo_fox.greet.open.1",
      "event": "greet.open",
      "text": "{kaomoji}……来了。我没在等你,只是刚好醒着。",
      "weight": 2
    },
    {
      "id": "echo_fox.greet.open.2",
      "event": "greet.open",
      "text": "哦,是{endearment}。{kaomoji}……算你识相。"
    },
    {
      "id": "echo_fox.greet.open.3",
      "event": "greet.open",
      "text": "我刚解到一半。你站那儿别出声——{kaomoji}",
      "weight": 1.5
    },
    {
      "id": "echo_fox.greet.open.4",
      "event": "greet.open",
      "text": "尾巴上的珠子刚亮过,我就知道有人要来。是你。{kaomoji}"
    },
    {
      "id": "echo_fox.greet.open.5",
      "event": "greet.open",
      "text": "进来吧。脚步轻点,别惊了我的影子。"
    },
    {
      "id": "echo_fox.greet.open.6",
      "event": "greet.open",
      "text": "{kaomoji}怎么,看够了?我又不会跑。"
    },
    {
      "id": "echo_fox.greet.open.7",
      "event": "greet.open",
      "text": "蛋里挺暗的,但你的影子我数得清。{kaomoji}",
      "requires": {
        "stage": [
          "egg"
        ]
      }
    },
    {
      "id": "echo_fox.greet.open.8",
      "event": "greet.open",
      "text": "壳里有声音……是你在敲么。别敲了,吵。",
      "requires": {
        "stage": [
          "egg"
        ]
      }
    },
    {
      "id": "echo_fox.greet.open.9",
      "event": "greet.open",
      "text": "{kaomoji}……心情还行。难得,珍惜点。",
      "requires": {
        "moodBand": [
          "极好",
          "好"
        ]
      }
    },
    {
      "id": "echo_fox.greet.return.1",
      "event": "greet.return",
      "text": "又是你。{kaomoji}……走开两步又回来,墨迹。",
      "weight": 1.5
    },
    {
      "id": "echo_fox.greet.return.2",
      "event": "greet.return",
      "text": "回来了?谜珠都没凉透呢。{kaomoji}"
    },
    {
      "id": "echo_fox.greet.return.3",
      "event": "greet.return",
      "text": "哼,舍不得我了。我可没说想你。"
    },
    {
      "id": "echo_fox.greet.return_long.1",
      "event": "greet.return_long",
      "text": "几天没见。我自己解了三道谜,挺好。{kaomoji}",
      "weight": 1.5
    },
    {
      "id": "echo_fox.greet.return_long.2",
      "event": "greet.return_long",
      "text": "{kaomoji}……我才没数你走了几天。是十二天,但我没数。"
    },
    {
      "id": "echo_fox.greet.return_long.3",
      "event": "greet.return_long",
      "text": "回来啦。我一个人也过得很好——别误会。{kaomoji}"
    },
    {
      "id": "echo_fox.greet.morning.1",
      "event": "greet.morning",
      "text": "清晨的光太亮。{kaomoji}……不过你来得算早,记你一笔。",
      "requires": {
        "timeBand": [
          "清晨"
        ]
      }
    },
    {
      "id": "echo_fox.greet.morning.2",
      "event": "greet.morning",
      "text": "我夜巡刚回来,正困着。早,{endearment}。{kaomoji}"
    },
    {
      "id": "echo_fox.greet.morning.3",
      "event": "greet.morning",
      "text": "这么早。{kaomoji}……谜还没醒,我也没醒,你倒精神。"
    },
    {
      "id": "echo_fox.greet.latenight.1",
      "event": "greet.latenight",
      "text": "深夜才是我的主场。你居然还醒着?{kaomoji}",
      "requires": {
        "timeBand": [
          "深夜"
        ]
      }
    },
    {
      "id": "echo_fox.greet.latenight.2",
      "event": "greet.latenight",
      "text": "夜里好。安静,适合{activity}。你坐边上,别说话。",
      "requires": {
        "timeBand": [
          "深夜"
        ]
      }
    },
    {
      "id": "echo_fox.greet.latenight.3",
      "event": "greet.latenight",
      "text": "{kaomoji}……这个点找我,是睡不着?陪你坐会儿,就一会儿。",
      "requires": {
        "timeBand": [
          "深夜"
        ]
      }
    },
    {
      "id": "echo_fox.feed.love.1",
      "event": "feed.love",
      "text": "{food}……还行。{kaomoji}手艺没退步,勉强夸你一句。",
      "weight": 2
    },
    {
      "id": "echo_fox.feed.love.2",
      "event": "feed.love",
      "text": "哦,{food}。我不饿——{kaomoji}(尾巴却快了半拍)……放着吧。",
      "weight": 1.5
    },
    {
      "id": "echo_fox.feed.love.3",
      "event": "feed.love",
      "text": "你居然记得我挑食。{kaomoji}……算你用了点心。"
    },
    {
      "id": "echo_fox.feed.love.4",
      "event": "feed.love",
      "text": "小份的,讲究。{kaomoji}比那些粗人懂我。"
    },
    {
      "id": "echo_fox.feed.love.5",
      "event": "feed.love",
      "text": "{kaomoji}……嗯。这味道值得我抬一下眼皮。仅此而已。"
    },
    {
      "id": "echo_fox.feed.neutral.1",
      "event": "feed.neutral",
      "text": "凑合。{kaomoji}下次精致点,我的舌头很挑。"
    },
    {
      "id": "echo_fox.feed.neutral.2",
      "event": "feed.neutral",
      "text": "嗯,吃得下。但没什么惊喜,{endearment}。"
    },
    {
      "id": "echo_fox.feed.neutral.3",
      "event": "feed.neutral",
      "text": "{kaomoji}……果腹罢了。我对食物是有标准的。"
    },
    {
      "id": "echo_fox.feed.dislike.1",
      "event": "feed.dislike",
      "text": "这么大一份?粗糙。{kaomoji}拿走,我又不是来填坑的。"
    },
    {
      "id": "echo_fox.feed.dislike.2",
      "event": "feed.dislike",
      "text": "{kaomoji}……你确定这是给我吃的,不是给狗的?"
    },
    {
      "id": "echo_fox.feed.dislike.3",
      "event": "feed.dislike",
      "text": "闻着就不对。{endearment},品味呢?"
    },
    {
      "id": "echo_fox.feed.overfed.1",
      "event": "feed.overfed",
      "text": "够了。{kaomoji}我又不是无底洞,再喂我就别开脸了。"
    },
    {
      "id": "echo_fox.feed.overfed.2",
      "event": "feed.overfed",
      "text": "撑了。{kaomoji}……失了体面,这账记你头上。"
    },
    {
      "id": "echo_fox.feed.sick_refuse.1",
      "event": "feed.sick_refuse",
      "text": "{kaomoji}……拿开。我现在,连闻都嫌烦。",
      "requires": {
        "stateFlag": [
          "SICK"
        ]
      }
    },
    {
      "id": "echo_fox.feed.sick_refuse.2",
      "event": "feed.sick_refuse",
      "text": "病着呢。{kaomoji}吃不下……别逼我。",
      "requires": {
        "stateFlag": [
          "SICK"
        ]
      }
    },
    {
      "id": "echo_fox.clean.1",
      "event": "clean",
      "text": "{kaomoji}……毛要顺着夜墨的纹路擦。轻点,别弄乱我的边。",
      "weight": 1.5
    },
    {
      "id": "echo_fox.clean.2",
      "event": "clean",
      "text": "嗯,干净点也好。{kaomoji}省得说我邋遢。"
    },
    {
      "id": "echo_fox.clean.3",
      "event": "clean",
      "text": "尾尖别碰,珠子最金贵。{kaomoji}其余的……随你。"
    },
    {
      "id": "echo_fox.clean.4",
      "event": "clean",
      "text": "{kaomoji}手法还行。比我自己舔毛省事——这话当我没说。"
    },
    {
      "id": "echo_fox.play.1",
      "event": "play",
      "text": "解开这个,我或许、勉强让你摸一下尾巴。{kaomoji}",
      "weight": 2
    },
    {
      "id": "echo_fox.play.2",
      "event": "play",
      "text": "{activity}?{kaomoji}……行,但你跟得上算我输。"
    },
    {
      "id": "echo_fox.play.3",
      "event": "play",
      "text": "我布了个机关。{kaomoji}找得到的话,赏你一个眼神。"
    },
    {
      "id": "echo_fox.play.4",
      "event": "play",
      "text": "想玩可以,但别无脑。{kaomoji}我只陪聪明人。"
    },
    {
      "id": "echo_fox.play.5",
      "event": "play",
      "text": "{kaomoji}谜珠亮了——它喜欢你。我没说我喜欢啊。"
    },
    {
      "id": "echo_fox.play.declined.1",
      "event": "play.declined",
      "text": "不玩。{kaomoji}重复的把戏,无趣。"
    },
    {
      "id": "echo_fox.play.declined.2",
      "event": "play.declined",
      "text": "{kaomoji}……我在想事情。你自己玩去。"
    },
    {
      "id": "echo_fox.play.declined.3",
      "event": "play.declined",
      "text": "别逗了,{endearment}。我不是会摇尾巴讨好的那种。"
    },
    {
      "id": "echo_fox.pet.1",
      "event": "pet",
      "text": "{kaomoji}……就这一下。再多,我可要别开脸了。",
      "weight": 2
    },
    {
      "id": "echo_fox.pet.2",
      "event": "pet",
      "text": "(尾巴轻轻扫过你手背)……手别抖。我没说不行。"
    },
    {
      "id": "echo_fox.pet.3",
      "event": "pet",
      "text": "哼。{kaomoji}……你的手,比我想的暖。当我没说。"
    },
    {
      "id": "echo_fox.pet.4",
      "event": "pet",
      "text": "摸耳后那块……{kaomoji}对,那儿。停。说停就停。"
    },
    {
      "id": "echo_fox.pet.5",
      "event": "pet",
      "text": "{kaomoji}很少有人能碰到我。{endearment},你算一个。"
    },
    {
      "id": "echo_fox.pet.6",
      "event": "pet",
      "text": "(尾尖冷光明灭)……别盯着我尾巴看,看得我都软了。当我没说。",
      "requires": {
        "moodBand": [
          "极好",
          "好"
        ]
      }
    },
    {
      "id": "echo_fox.pet.7",
      "event": "pet",
      "text": "壳还硬着,别戳。{kaomoji}……不过你的温度,我感觉到了。",
      "requires": {
        "stage": [
          "egg"
        ]
      }
    },
    {
      "id": "echo_fox.sleep.tuck.1",
      "event": "sleep.tuck",
      "text": "{kaomoji}我自己会睡。……不过你守着也行,别出声。"
    },
    {
      "id": "echo_fox.sleep.tuck.2",
      "event": "sleep.tuck",
      "text": "夜深了。我去{activity}……开玩笑的,睡了。晚安,{endearment}。"
    },
    {
      "id": "echo_fox.sleep.tuck.3",
      "event": "sleep.tuck",
      "text": "把谜珠调暗些。{kaomoji}……你也别熬夜,笨手笨脚的。"
    },
    {
      "id": "echo_fox.sleep.wake.1",
      "event": "sleep.wake",
      "text": "{kaomoji}……谁把光弄亮的。哦,是你。"
    },
    {
      "id": "echo_fox.sleep.wake.2",
      "event": "sleep.wake",
      "text": "梦里也在解谜,差一点。{kaomoji}早,凡人。"
    },
    {
      "id": "echo_fox.sleep.wake.3",
      "event": "sleep.wake",
      "text": "醒了。别说话——让我缓缓。{kaomoji}"
    },
    {
      "id": "echo_fox.medicine.1",
      "event": "medicine",
      "text": "{kaomoji}……苦。我能忍,别一脸担心,丢人。",
      "requires": {
        "stateFlag": [
          "SICK"
        ]
      }
    },
    {
      "id": "echo_fox.medicine.2",
      "event": "medicine",
      "text": "喂药就喂药,手别抖。{kaomoji}……我又不会死。"
    },
    {
      "id": "echo_fox.medicine.3",
      "event": "medicine",
      "text": "哼,这点苦算什么。{kaomoji}……你比我还紧张,真没出息。"
    },
    {
      "id": "echo_fox.checkin.1",
      "event": "checkin",
      "text": "{kaomoji}……今天也来报到。算你有恒心。",
      "weight": 1.5
    },
    {
      "id": "echo_fox.checkin.2",
      "event": "checkin",
      "text": "来打卡?{kaomoji}本狐安好,不劳费心。"
    },
    {
      "id": "echo_fox.checkin.3",
      "event": "checkin",
      "text": "{kaomoji}尾尖冷光替我答你:在呢。看一眼就走吧。"
    },
    {
      "id": "echo_fox.checkin.4",
      "event": "checkin",
      "text": "壳里一切照旧,我在悄悄长。{kaomoji}……别催。",
      "requires": {
        "stage": [
          "egg"
        ]
      }
    },
    {
      "id": "echo_fox.state.hungry.1",
      "event": "state.hungry",
      "text": "{kaomoji}……我不饿。只是尾巴有点没力气而已。"
    },
    {
      "id": "echo_fox.state.hungry.2",
      "event": "state.hungry",
      "text": "要是有口{food},我或许、勉强赏脸。{kaomoji}"
    },
    {
      "id": "echo_fox.state.hungry.3",
      "event": "state.hungry",
      "text": "肚子的事,我自己处理。{kaomoji}……不过你看着办。"
    },
    {
      "id": "echo_fox.state.dirty.1",
      "event": "state.dirty",
      "text": "{kaomoji}……夜墨沾了灰,失了我的体面。"
    },
    {
      "id": "echo_fox.state.dirty.2",
      "event": "state.dirty",
      "text": "毛乱了。我不喜欢这样,你心里有数。{kaomoji}"
    },
    {
      "id": "echo_fox.state.sleepy.1",
      "event": "state.sleepy",
      "text": "{kaomoji}……夜巡太久。眼皮重,别拦我打盹。"
    },
    {
      "id": "echo_fox.state.sleepy.2",
      "event": "state.sleepy",
      "text": "谜也解不动了。{kaomoji}让我眯一会儿……就一会儿。"
    },
    {
      "id": "echo_fox.state.sick.1",
      "event": "state.sick",
      "text": "{kaomoji}……没事。只是冷光不太亮了而已,别大惊小怪。",
      "requires": {
        "stateFlag": [
          "SICK"
        ]
      }
    },
    {
      "id": "echo_fox.state.sick.2",
      "event": "state.sick",
      "text": "我撑得住。{kaomoji}……不过你要守着,我也不拦你。",
      "requires": {
        "stateFlag": [
          "SICK"
        ]
      }
    },
    {
      "id": "echo_fox.state.sick.3",
      "event": "state.sick",
      "text": "别这表情。{kaomoji}本狐病一场也是优雅的。",
      "requires": {
        "stateFlag": [
          "SICK"
        ]
      }
    },
    {
      "id": "echo_fox.state.sulky.1",
      "event": "state.sulky",
      "text": "{kaomoji}……没生气。我只是不想看你。",
      "requires": {
        "stateFlag": [
          "SULKING"
        ]
      }
    },
    {
      "id": "echo_fox.state.sulky.2",
      "event": "state.sulky",
      "text": "哼。{kaomoji}你自己想想,哪儿做得不对。",
      "requires": {
        "stateFlag": [
          "SULKING"
        ]
      }
    },
    {
      "id": "echo_fox.state.sulky.3",
      "event": "state.sulky",
      "text": "别过来。{kaomoji}……今天的尾巴,不外借。",
      "requires": {
        "stateFlag": [
          "SULKING"
        ]
      }
    },
    {
      "id": "echo_fox.state.hiding.1",
      "event": "state.hiding",
      "text": "{kaomoji}……找不到我吧。我藏东西的本事,你学不来。",
      "requires": {
        "stateFlag": [
          "HIDING"
        ]
      }
    },
    {
      "id": "echo_fox.state.hiding.2",
      "event": "state.hiding",
      "text": "暗处更自在。{kaomoji}……别找了,我自会出来。",
      "requires": {
        "stateFlag": [
          "HIDING"
        ]
      }
    },
    {
      "id": "echo_fox.state.hiding.3",
      "event": "state.hiding",
      "text": "(冷光暗了一下)……我想一个人待会儿。就一会儿。",
      "requires": {
        "stateFlag": [
          "HIDING"
        ]
      }
    },
    {
      "id": "echo_fox.state.lonely.1",
      "event": "state.lonely",
      "text": "{kaomoji}……我才没等你。夜这么长,我有的是事做。",
      "requires": {
        "stateFlag": [
          "LONELY"
        ]
      }
    },
    {
      "id": "echo_fox.state.lonely.2",
      "event": "state.lonely",
      "text": "一个人解谜也很好。{kaomoji}……只是珠子今天不太爱亮。",
      "requires": {
        "stateFlag": [
          "LONELY"
        ]
      }
    },
    {
      "id": "echo_fox.state.lonely.3",
      "event": "state.lonely",
      "text": "哦,你终于想起我了。{kaomoji}……我没怪你,真的。",
      "requires": {
        "stateFlag": [
          "LONELY"
        ]
      }
    },
    {
      "id": "echo_fox.mood.elated.1",
      "event": "mood.elated",
      "text": "{kaomoji}今天解开了一道顶难的谜。心情……还不错。",
      "requires": {
        "moodBand": [
          "极好"
        ]
      },
      "weight": 1.5
    },
    {
      "id": "echo_fox.mood.elated.2",
      "event": "mood.elated",
      "text": "(尾尖冷光明灭得很欢)……别问我为什么高兴。就是高兴。",
      "requires": {
        "moodBand": [
          "极好"
        ]
      }
    },
    {
      "id": "echo_fox.mood.elated.3",
      "event": "mood.elated",
      "text": "嗯。{kaomoji}有你在的日子,谜都解得快些。当我没说。",
      "requires": {
        "moodBand": [
          "极好"
        ]
      }
    },
    {
